You are stealing from my boss.

41:03.954 --> 41:05.396
Don't mess with me.

41:05.421 --> 41:06.838
Carter?

41:06.863 --> 41:09.349
I don't want you working there anymore.

41:09.374 --> 41:10.573
It's not your call.

41:10.598 --> 41:11.667
The parties are over.

41:11.693 --> 41:12.547
Have you seen Taylor?

41:12.572 --> 41:14.689
Gabe told me that he has feelings for me.

